# GhostLaw Backend

## Free-tier stack:
# - Google Gemini 2.0 Flash (free: 15 RPM, 1M tokens/day)
# - Supabase (free: 500MB DB, 50K auth users)
# - Vercel (free deployment)

## Environment variables needed:
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_free_key_from_aistudio.google.com
# SUPABASE_URL=your_project_url
# SUPABASE_KEY=your_anon_key
# JWT_SECRET=use_a_long_random_secret_at_least_32_chars
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_oauth_client_id
# APPLE_CLIENT_ID=your_apple_service_id
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://app.example.com,https://preview.example.com,http://localhost:3000
# APP_ENV=development
# DEBUG=true
